  audioProfileName: 
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Good Work recruit!  The bunny menace is dealt with and you look
      pretty spiffy in your new armor.


      Kung Fu alone won''t be enough to
      win this battle though.


      You will need to train your other skills too.'
    nextOption: Other Skills?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You can channel the power of the Sun more effectively wearing robes
      and using gems to focus the light.


      You can even use it to heal yourself
      and allies!'
    nextOption: Without burning them?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Yes, and I will require your help to defeat those undead blocking
      the entrance to the camp.


      They look much tougher than the bunnies.


      You
      will need some heavier armor and weapons.'
    nextOption: But you said you didn't have any to spare
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You are in luck!


      We have all the raw ingredients you will
      need right here in the camp.'
    nextOption: Phew
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'All you need to do is learn Mining, Herbalism, and Logging.


      Then
      once you have collected the materials, you can train in BlackSmithing, Jewelry,
      Tailoring, and Woodworking.'
    nextOption: Oh is that all?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Use the skills to make a Shiny Suit of Armor to defend against
      attacks.


      Craft a Dragon Blade to cut down your enemies.


      You
      will also need some Fine Robes and an Initiate''s Staff to empower your Chanelling
      abilities.

'
    nextOption: Um, how long will this take?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Go talk to the apprentice again.


      He will give you the details
      on the needed ingredients.


      He will also show you how to find and collect
      them.'
    nextOption: Yes Sir
  prerequisiteConditions: []
